Create a simplistic engine for the plugin to run off of:

This engine should:
ret empty start,validate,and next_task fns
def engine.start(mode, difficulty) & store in state

create buf
create win

 + bufhidden=wipe (for cleanup)

build state with buf, win, diff, start time, cursor movement (var to change during mode), task ID
add state into engine

create an autocmd group for CursorMoved,TextChanged,InsertLeave to call validate if needed
Add an autocmd for WinClosed to clean up

-----
loop:
mode.on_start -> setup logic
mode.on_task_start -> spawn task
engine.validate -> check if finished
                -> engine.next_task -> mode.on_task_end -> regen buf
                                                        -> start of loop
